    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey US America<ptr target="uva.00492_n1"
                        /></name>
                    <date when="1886-08-02" rend="right">Aug: 2 '86</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>A pleasant forenoon as I write, here by the open window. I remain ab't as
                usual&#8212;a little pull'd down by the heat perhaps. Your letter came, &#38; was
                welcome, as always&#8212;Alys's "circular"<ptr target="uva.00492_n2"/> came, &#38;
                now one from Romsey arrived this morn'g&#8212;I had a letter from Dr B[ucke] two
                days ago&#8212; all well&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
